43:39.148 --> 43:41.344
- Okay? All right.
- All right.

44:08.111 --> 44:09.738
I hope they don't get fucking lost.

44:16.018 --> 44:17.849
Fuck me! Ten-million bucks.

44:20.455 --> 44:22.685
The joke is,
say we dipped in, took some?

44:22.858 --> 44:25.793
