living in a halfway house in Queens.

53:10.101 --> 53:13.468
He's not an absconder, he made his
appearances, his piss has been clean.

53:13.638 --> 53:16.630
But he was a no-show at work today.
He didn't call in, nothing.

53:16.807 --> 53:18.638
He knows the system.

53:18.809 --> 53:21.073
The perfect place in the subway
to stop the train.

53:21.245 --> 53:23.975
He's been out a month.
This wasn't planned in three weeks.

53:24.148 --> 53:27.172
Find out Ramos's cellmates,
who worked in the laundry with him.

53:27.349 --> 53:29.647
Call lists, visitors lists ASAP.

53:41.730 --> 53:42.889
<i>105 North Avenue.</i>

53:53.508 --> 53:54.634
- Shit! Look out!
- Shit!

54:05.452 --> 54:07.353
<i>The market has tumbled
nearly 7 percent...</i>

54:07.522 --> 54:09.581
<i>... as investors continue
to react to events...</i>

54:09.757 --> 54:11.156
They just came off the bridge.

54:11.325 --> 54:14.352
Why didn't we send
a helicopter for the money?

54:16.264 --> 54:19.131
Now remember what I said
about talking through deadlines.

54:19.300 --> 54:22.929
We better have a plan B in case
the money isn't there on the dot.

54:23.104 --> 54:24.901
Put him on his heels.
He knows things.

54:25.073 --> 54:26.938
- We know things too, right?
- Right.

54:27.108 --> 54:30.135
Ask him about Phil Ramos. All right?
Just get him talking.

54:30.312 --> 54:31.336
You can do it.

54:35.516 --> 54:37.450
- Hey, Ryder.
- The money here yet?

54:37.618 --> 54:38.642
<i>On the way.</i>

54:38.820 --> 54:40.981
Then what the fuck
are you calling me for?

54:41.155 --> 54:43.055
Actually, I just called to talk.

54:44.192 --> 54:46.353
<i>Oh, yeah?
What do you wanna talk about?</i>

54:47.128 --> 54:50.392
You said that
being in the motorman's cab...

54:50.564 --> 54:52.964
...was a little like
being in a confessional, right?

54:53.133 --> 54:54.157
Yeah?

54:54.334 --> 54:57.167
I was thinking maybe it's like
being in a prison cell too.

54:57.337 --> 55:00.829
What are you trying to say? That
if I get caught, I'd better get used to it?

55:01.007 --> 55:03.703
No, I'm just wondering.
Maybe you're already used to it.

55:03.877 --> 55:08.438
I'm wondering maybe that's how
you meet a guy like Phil Ramos?

55:08.614 --> 55:10.241
How the fuck he know that?

55:10.416 --> 55:12.441
Why don't you tell me?
Then we'll both know.

55:12.618 --> 55:13.915
After today's confession...

55:14.086 --> 55:16.077
<i>... you're gonna find your ass
in prison too.</i>

55:16.255 --> 55:18.917
Which is my point. I want you
to hook me up on the inside.

55:19.091 --> 55:22.218
You know everybody. This way,
when I come up with my heist plan...

55:22.393 --> 55:24.362
...you know, I'll cut you in.

55:24.530 --> 55:27.158
I can see I've inspired you.
Okay, I got a story for you.

55:27.333 --> 55:30.302
<i>It might help you in prison.
You wanna hear it? We got a minute.</i>

55:30.469 --> 55:31.936
I'd like to hear a little story.

55:32.104 --> 55:34.698
<i>So back in the day,
when I was a high roller...</i>

55:34.874 --> 55:36.398
When were you ever a high roller?

55:38.042 --> 55:40.033
<i>I told you I fed this city breakfast.</i>

55:40.211 --> 55:41.235
Grits and eggs?

55:41.412 --> 55:43.539
Something like that.
Anyway, back in the day...

55:43.715 --> 55:46.115
...I took this chick to Iceland.

55:46.417 --> 55:48.886
Iceland? Is that where
all the high rollers go?

55:49.054 --> 55:52.114
Six hours from Kennedy
and the nightclub scene is...

55:52.291 --> 55:53.519
