01:36:18.912 --> 01:36:21.512
- Come on, man, pay it back.
- I'm not gonna shoot you.

01:36:21.712 --> 01:36:23.513
I'm gonna give you 10,
then deal's off.

01:36:23.713 --> 01:36:27.014
