Come on, motherfucker, shoot me!

01:36:40.114 --> 01:36:42.314
I am not going to shoot you!

01:36:43.413 --> 01:36:46.215
Five, four. Come on.

01:36:46.314 --> 01:36:48.415
- Hey!
- Three.

01:36:48.716 --> 01:36:50.016
Police, drop your weapon!

01:36:50.216 --> 01:36:52.716
I'm disappointed in you. Two.

01:37:02.717 --> 01:37:04.917
You're my goddamn hero.

01:37:16.018 --> 01:37:17.919
Drop your weapon!

01:38:03.121 --> 01:38:04.722
Mr. Garber.

01:38:07.122 --> 01:38:09.222
- Interesting day, huh?
- Yes, sir.

01:38:09.421 --> 01:38:11.923
