I make a speech...

01:38:12.123 --> 01:38:14.323
...and it starts with:

01:38:14.523 --> 01:38:18.123
"I'd like to thank you on behalf of
the city of New York," blah, blah, blah.

01:38:18.223 --> 01:38:20.925
