who I'm thanking or why.

01:38:21.425 --> 01:38:22.525
But you...

01:38:23.827 --> 01:38:25.327
...did a hell of a thing today.

01:38:25.526 --> 01:38:27.826
You went to bat
for the city of New York.

01:38:27.926 --> 01:38:30.926
And on behalf of me,
I'd like to thank you.

01:38:31.826 --> 01:38:34.926
